Title: Jump-Diffusion Enhanced Black–Scholes for European Options

Problem:
1. Black–Scholes assumes continuous price paths
2. Real markets experience sudden jumps (earnings, policy shocks, geopolitical events)
3. Leads to systematic mispricing → hidden risks

Solution:
1. Extend BS with Jump-Diffusion process
2. Captures discrete jumps + continuous movements
3. Balances realism with speed for trading desks

Stakeholders:
1. Risk Management Lead → compliance & governance
2. Options Traders / Quants → fast & accurate hedging + execution
3. Deliverables

Baseline BS pricing tool:
1. Jump-Diffusion model with calibration
2. Python API for traders & risk teams
3. Validation report (accuracy, robustness, runtime)